(1, '20160501/57255ec5bc84a.jpg', '厂家直销1111网格九脚托盘 佛山塑料托盘 广东塑料托盘出口专用', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">产品说明：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">1.采用全新、水口或再生HDPE、PP塑胶原料注塑一体成型。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">2.耐用、抗冲击、防潮防腐烂、韧性好、方便使用等特点，属于无毒环保产品。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">3.常规蓝色、黑色、可定制绿色、红色、黄色、灰色等颜色产品。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">4.可以印LOGO，订做各种颜色。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">产品实物图：</span></span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><img alt="undefined" height="562.5" src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/645/459/2176954546_699245856.jpg" width="750" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 790px; zoom: 1;"/><br/><img alt="undefined" height="562.5" src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/665/459/2176954566_699245856.jpg" width="750" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 790px; zoom: 1;"/><br/></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.5;">生产车间：</span></span></span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">&nbsp;<img alt="20140523181535" height="464.5522388059701" src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/983/952/2089259389_699245856.jpg" width="750" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 790px; zoom: 1;"/></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">成品仓库：</span></span><span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14pt; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">&nbsp;</span><img alt="20140523181450" height="464.5522388059701" src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/883/193/2088391388_699245856.jpg" width="750" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 790px; zoom: 1;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">塑料托盘｜塑胶卡板、栈板的应用：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">适用于服装、机械、电子、塑胶、食品、水产、物流、仓储、高科技电子五金行业、或用于医疗行业、长途运输等，车间长期周转和一次性出口使用，满足客户各方面的需求。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">塑料托盘｜塑胶卡板、栈板的产品特性：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(1）四面可插，操作方便；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(2）既适合在仓库中互相堆垛，又适合在各类货架上使用；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(3）适合各类卡车运输，方便物料的集装化、单元化运输；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(4）方便叉车、液压托盘车等搬运工具作业；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(5）配合防滑橡胶，保证物料在搬运和运输过程中不会滑落；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(6）使用寿命长，且可循坏再用；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(7）防潮防蛀、无毒无味、耐磨损、耐酸耐碱、抗冲击一次注塑型。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">购买需知：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">一：请广大客户在下单购买我公司任何产品前、能先联系我，询问需购买的商品情况、运输等一些情况，这样才能让您准确的获知商品的情况，也才能减少与避免不必要的误会。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">二：关于价格问题旺铺上所有商品均为参考价，根据行情价格会有上涨或下调&nbsp;量大可申请优惠&nbsp;商品的价格问题需与我们电话或旺旺联系。欢迎朋友们来我公司考察。我们遵守量大从优的原则。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">物流快递说明：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;一：外省可发物流一般3~5天可到货。(运费另算)</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;二：珠三角内量大可加厂车送货。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;三：产品订量少则发快递。(费用详情请来电咨询)</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0);

